<H3> <TI>   Beijing Selects 30 `Model Families' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Beijing Selects 30 `Model Families' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1305130594 Beijing XINHUA in English 0833 GMT 13 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1305130594 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, May 13 (XINHUA) -- Thirty families from 
different parts of the country were chosen as the country's 
"model families" here today. 
  It was the third such selection and was significant as this 
year is the "International Year of the Family". 
  The selection is aimed at promoting the development of 
family 
culture and guiding people to pursue a civilized, healthy and 
scientific lifestyle, said Chen Muhua, vice-chairwoman of the 
Standing Committee of the National People's Congress and 
president of the All-China Women's Federation (ACWF) at an award 
ceremony held for the model families here today. 
  The 30 families represent a happy family atmosphere and 
colorful family life. All the family members are actively 
taking part in China's economic construction and making 
contributions to society, said Chen. 
  Among the 30 families, ten were awarded gold and silver 
prizes and 20 awarded honorary prizes through a public ballot 
and specialists' appraisal, according to Chen. 
  The selection process was jointly organized by the ACWF and 
China central television, and financially supported by an 
enterprise in Sichuan Province. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

